snippet.title: Wanadev Studio - Official Ragnarok Jonathan Young DLC & Vestiges Trailer
snippet.description: Ragnarock's next DLC will be dedicated to Jonathan Young, available on PC and all major VR platforms on December 14. Additionally, get a first look at Wanadev Studio's next game called Vestiges: Fallen Tribe, an upcoming strategy card game mixed with an auto-battler. Vestiges: Fallen Tribe will be set in a sci-fi universe and features PVP battles. A demo for Vestiges: Fallen Tribe will be available in January 2024.
